Body: Hello! I've been reading your whitepaper, and I'm curious about how are going to implement it. As far as I know, Ethereum transaction fees are rather high now, so my concern is that it would be quite expensive for advertisers and customers to use your platform. How do you solve this problem?

Author: CBJon
Title: [ANN] [TokenSale/ICO] ğŸš€ Cashbag.io Token Sale 15% Bonus ğŸš€ ForkDelta Exchange ğŸ‘ğŸ»
Body: Thank you for your query. Unfortunately we were forced to suspend all the bounty program activity. The Bounty manager is no longer actively involved and we are internally managing the program. The stakes were assigned on the spreadsheet through to the end of the last week the program ran and it was announced.  Once the token sale is complete we will be closing out and calculating the stakes and issuing the tokens, as per the bounty agreement. Thank you for participating.

Author: CBJon
Title: [ANN] [TokenSale/ICO] ğŸš€ Cashbag.io Token Sale 15% Bonus ğŸš€ ForkDelta Exchange ğŸ‘ğŸ»
Body: That's a really good question!  Actually, compared to bank fees, Ethereum tx fees are still very low, so we're able to very favorably compete. We can of course do settlement at a lower priority as well, so we don't always need to compete with the high priority transactions that are taking up higher gas fees when we process, our tx's can wait a little longer to complete.  There are also other solutions, like batching the transactions together, but we're in favor of more realtime approaches to settlement ;-)

With over 130K users and growing, CashBag is issuing a token sale to enable it's Advertisers to pay for advertising and consumers to earn tokens as rewards for transacting through CashBag. Author: CBJon
Title: [ANN] [TokenSale/ICO] ğŸš€ Cashbag.io Token Sale 15% Bonus ğŸš€ ForkDelta Exchange ğŸ‘ğŸ»
Body: THE TOKEN UTILITY     PAY FOR ADVERTISING ON CASHBAG Merchants and advertisers offering services and products on CashBag can pay their advertising fees using the token. Advertising is paid in local currency and through the token sale early adopters are guaranteed their US$ equivalent token value in advertising services in their local market. As token value increases any redemptions will be valued at current market prices, effectively guaranteeing a discounted rate on advertising in the platform for early crowd sale adopters.   EARNING INCENTIVES & REWARDS CashBag members earn tokens each time they transact via the CashBag platform and purchase from a participating merchant. Initially, for every $1 or local market equivalent earned in cash back rewards the consumer will earn an additional 10% bonus ($0.10) in CBC.   GAMIFICATION / REWARDS Members who choose to opt-in may earn tokens for acting on and sharing curated content and interesting information ranging from news stories to videos, movie or product launches. On our platform, the end user benefits directly from viewing and engaging the content and is no longer considered just a product, but becomes an active participant in the transaction process.   TRADING THE TOKEN The token can be freely traded, exchanged and sold. CashBag will honor the crowd sale issued tokens for advertising services at the guaranteed discount rate through the smart contract rules. The token may trade on multiple exchanges and as an ERC20 compliant token may be stored in any compliant wallet and used for purchases.  DEBIT CARD The addition of a linked VISA/MASTERCARD debit card will enable members to transact globally, using CBC to purchase at real world merchants, withdraw cash and instantaneously access their funds using just in time (JIT) funding.  SENDING MONEY / MAKING PAYMENTS The token can be used to send money to CashBag members or make payments through smart contracts initiated by users on the CashBag platform and beyond. Within the CashBag marketplace members will be able to gift tokens, pay for services, buy products from the CashBag marketplace and eventually purchase goods from integrated merchant partners who accept payments from ERC20 wallets in general and CashBag specifically.  WALLET CashBag members can request / send CBC between members and pay for services on the platform. The wallet is ERC20 compliant so funds can be transferred out of our ecosystem and used in other wallets.   THE MEMBER HAS THE OPTION TO RECEIVE PAYOUTS IN: All in Fiat (CBC will be immediately traded and cash equivalent held in their CashBag account until payout) CashBag rewards in FIAT and incentives in CBC Tokens All in CBC Tokens
